Food Delivery App UI 

1️⃣ **Login Screen**

\- Secure login page  

\- Email \& password fields  

\- Login button with primary color  

\- “Create new account” link  



&nbsp;2️⃣ **Signup Screen**

\- User registration form  

\- Input fields for username, email, and password  

\- Confirmation button  



3️⃣ **Onboarding Screens**

\- Introductory walkthrough for new users  

\- Illustrations + short descriptions  

\- “Next” \& “Get Started” buttons  



4️⃣ **Home Screen**

\- Search bar for food items  

\- Categories (Pizza, Burgers, Drinks, etc.)  

\- Popular and recommended dishes  

\- Modern card-style layout  



5️⃣ **Food Items Screen**

\- List of available dishes  

\- Images, prices, and ratings  

\- Add-to-cart buttons  



&nbsp;6️⃣ **Cart Screen**

\- All selected items  

\- Quantity control  

\- Total price calculation  

\- Checkout button  



7️⃣ **Delivery Tracking Screen**

\- Real-time order status  

\- Delivery time estimate  

\- Delivery partner details  



8️⃣ **Success / Order Confirmation Screen**

\- After placing an order  

\- Green success tick  

\- "Order Placed Successfully" message  



